description: This file defines data transfer objects (DTOs) for authentication operations such as sign-up, login, and authentication response in a notes management backend system.

inner_classes.name: SignUpRequest
inner_classes.description: DTO for sign-up requests containing username and password.

inner_classes.name: LoginRequest
inner_classes.description: DTO for login requests containing username and password.

inner_classes.name: AuthResponse
inner_classes.description: DTO for authentication responses containing a JWT token and username.

methods.name: AuthResponse
methods.description: Constructor for creating an AuthResponse object with token and username.
